1) Firmware version
post v1.0:
- cancel request (0xC3) enabled by default
- added get description command (0xD5)
- eeprom param: add adjustable delay after manual typing
- for MMM: allow the get_login command to already specify the login
- eeprom param: allow customization of key sent after login AND password manual entry
post v1.1:
- added a "user db change number" updated upon db changes, to make sync notifications (can be read/written using 0xD6 & 0xD4)
- added new command to know how many free slots for new users there are (0xD7)

2) Device specific
- eeprom param: knock detection enable & sensitivity
- eeprom param: screen luminosity
